This blue dusters refills for cleaning can be used by anyone.it is suitable for cleaning the dust in sofas, tables, ceilings, shutters, ceiling fans, circuit boards, bookcases, bottom of sofa, bottom of bed, bottom of cabinet, wall gap, wall surface, bathroom, stove, etc. Shake and rub the disposable duster head before use, it will be more fluffy and adsorption capacity will be more powerful. Disposable duster refills can be thrown away after use that makes housework more effective.
